{"tid":2037190,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「港區國安法」未立法已收緊","createTime":"2020-05-27T00:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T01:40:11.000Z","uid":85502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b937d081f7292f72e28f6ee27cd6dfd2d3c88c6","tid":2037190,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:44:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528451-20200526.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528451-20200526.htm&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=f12c1f11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528451-20200526.htm&h=e1563c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528451-20200526.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大下午審議常委會建立「港區國安法」和健全執行機制的決定草案修改稿，據了解，草案有數處修改。<br />\n<br />\n修改稿獲會議主席團開會通過，據了解，決定草案原本提到「禁止危害國安的行為」的相關内容，最新版本都改為「禁止危害國安的行為和活動」，增加「活動」的概念。<br />\n<br />\n至於較受爭議的第4項決定，有關中央維護國安的機關可能在港設立機構的内容，則沒有改動。<br />\n<br />\n根據議程，人大星期四早上會審議決定草案的建議表決稿，當天下午在閉幕會上進行表決。"},{"pid":"d476dbe47d8af52acc4ceb0efb006c03b13f67f9","tid":2037190,"uid":215881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"香港一步步俾侵蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b42e5b2cd710d97a4e657e416a6afaf4b73082c","tid":2037190,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad642f9b2490061fc6c2b4dddde7493c91d9071","tid":2037190,"uid":41974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d476dbe47d8af52acc4ceb0efb006c03b13f67f9","tid":2037190,"uid":215881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"香港一步步俾侵蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:46:55.000Z"